    <decisions>
        <description>Requirement : If the curstomer opts out Pre OBE we want to Clear, after then we leave as if. The identifier for OBE is Billing Onboarding Eligible Date. So the logic would be:

If Billing Onboarding Eligible Date is NULL and Billing Opt Out Override is marked True then Clear BASD.
If Billing Onboarding Eligible Date is NOT NULL and Billing Opt Out Override is marked True then leave BASD as is.</description>
        <name>Opted_Out_Pre_OBE</name>
        <label>Opted Out Pre OBE</label>
        <locationX>182</locationX>
        <locationY>971</locationY>
        <defaultConnector>
            <targetReference>Subflow_Sync_Opportunity_Post_CW_Stage</targetReference>
        </defaultConnector>
        <defaultConnectorLabel>Default Outcome</defaultConnectorLabel>
        <rules>
            <name>Billing_Onboarding_Eligible_Date_is_NULL</name>
            <conditionLogic>and</conditionLogic>
            <conditions>
                <leftValueReference>Get_Account.Billing_Onboarding_Eligible_Date__c</leftValueReference>
                <operator>IsNull</operator>
                <rightValue>
                    <booleanValue>true</booleanValue>
                </rightValue>
            </conditions>
            <connector>
                <targetReference>Update_Account</targetReference>
            </connector>
            <label>Billing Onboarding Eligible Date is NULL</label>
        </rules>
    </decisions>
