    <description>Updates Opportunity Post CW Stages based on triggers on the Opportunity Object such as the Billing Opt Out Override and OBS Scheduled Date

04.15.2025 - Added the logic to update the combined funnel when Billing Opt-in Override  is changed to True !
04.17.2025 - LK - New field was created &quot; Billing Opt Out Override Reason&quot; , remapped it on the update combined funnel node.
04.22.2025 - LK - Only clear out Billing Activation Start Date  if Billing Onboarding Eligible Date is NULL
04.29.2025 - LK - Updated Entry Condition to trigger when - FLOW - Participant Sequence History - After Save - Update Opp Post CW Stages &gt;&gt; nulls out POST CW STATUS from &quot; unresponsive&quot; status to allow the opportunity to be reassessed accurately
05.05.2025 - Update logic trigger flow  - to when Approved_Accelerated_Onboarding_Date__c OR Approved_OBE_Override_Date__c are populated.</description>
